Type hints:  
- [Python docs – typing](https://docs.python.org/3/library/typing.html)  
- [PEP 484 – Type Hints](https://peps.python.org/pep-0484/)  
- [mypy – Cheat Sheet (Python 3)](https://mypy.readthedocs.io/en/stable/cheat_sheet_py3.html)  

Docstrings:  
- [PEP 257 – Docstring Conventions](https://peps.python.org/pep-0257/)  
- [Python docs – Documentation Strings](https://docs.python.org/3/tutorial/controlflow.html#tut-docstrings)  

Style:  
- [PEP 8 – Style Guide for Python Code](https://peps.python.org/pep-0008/)

